items.bio: Runner from Singapore. I am a friendly guy.
像是一場夢，醒了一切都消失了.. 下雨天真的很美~ 讓我成為你的人魚公主吧.. 愛過.. 然後靜靜的消失.. 雙魚座 ♡
Completed my year 2017 36th full marathon at Osim Sundown Marathon Singapore after my last full marathon in December 2016. Feeling great!
Chief Eating Officer of Lion City Vegetarian Food Blog @ www.littlegreenwok.sg and Howler for Singapore Vegetarian Food page
